<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Event Feedback Request - {{eventTitle}}</title>
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family:
          'Inter',
          -apple-system,
          BlinkMacSystemFont,
          'Segoe UI',
          Roboto,
          sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #ffffff;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f23 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
        padding: 16px;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ec4899 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
        padding: 24px 32px 20px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(
          90deg,
          transparent 0%,
          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 50%,
          transparent 100%
        );
        transform: translateX(-100%);
        animation: shine 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      @keyframes shine {
        0% {
          transform: translateX(-100%);
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateX(100%);
        }
        100% {
          transform: translateX(100%);
        }
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      }

      .logo::before {
        content: '</>';
        font-size: 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f472b6, #a855f7);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
      }

      .header h1 {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin: 0;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      }

      .header h1::before {
        content: '// ';
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
      }

      .content {
        padding: 32px;
      }

      .feedback-hero {
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15) 0%,
          rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 100%
        );
        border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 32px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .feedback-hero::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 2px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #22c55e, #8b5cf6, #a855f7, #22c55e);
        background-size: 300% 100%;
        animation: feedbackShift 3s ease infinite;
      }

      @keyframes feedbackShift {
        0%,
        100% {
          background-position: 0% 50%;
        }
        50% {
          background-position: 100% 50%;
        }
      }

      .feedback-icon {
        font-size: 64px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        display: block;
        animation: celebrate 3s ease infinite;
      }

      @keyframes celebrate {
        0%,
        100% {
          transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg);
        }
        25% {
          transform: scale(1.05) rotate(-3deg);
        }
        50% {
          transform: scale(1.02) rotate(0deg);
        }
        75% {
          transform: scale(1.05) rotate(3deg);
        }
      }

      .feedback-title {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 700;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #22c55e, #8b5cf6, #a855f7);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .feedback-subtitle {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.9);
        font-weight: 500;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      }

      .event-title {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 0%,
          rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.1) 100%
        );
        border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 16px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .greeting {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .description {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .highlight {
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1) 0%,
          rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 100%
        );
        border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .highlight::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 2px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #22c55e, #8b5cf6, #a855f7, #22c55e);
        background-size: 300% 100%;
        animation: highlightShift 4s ease infinite;
      }

      @keyframes highlightShift {
        0%,
        100% {
          background-position: 0% 50%;
        }
        50% {
          background-position: 100% 50%;
        }
      }

      .highlight h3 {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .highlight h3::before {
        content: '💡';
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .cta-section {
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          #22c55e 0%,
          #8b5cf6 50%,
          #a855f7 100%
        );
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 24px 0;
        color: #ffffff;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .cta-section::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(
          45deg,
          transparent 30%,
          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 50%,
          transparent 70%
        );
        transform: translateX(-100%);
        animation: ctaShine 4s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      @keyframes ctaShine {
        0% {
          transform: translateX(-100%);
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateX(100%);
        }
        100% {
          transform: translateX(100%);
        }
      }

      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 12px 32px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 16px;
        border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .cta-button:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }

      .organizer-info {
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.6) 0%,
          rgba(55, 65, 81, 0.6) 100%
        );
        border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .organizer-info p {
        margin: 8px 0;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      }

      .organizer-name {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.9);
      }

      .security-note {
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1) 0%,
          rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 100%
        );
        border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 16px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.9);
        text-align: center;
      }

      .security-note::before {
        content: '🔒 ';
        margin-right: 6px;
      }

      .footer {
        background: linear-gradient(
          135deg,
          rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.8) 0%,
          rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.8) 100%
        );
        padding: 24px 32px;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
      }

      .footer-brand {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      }

      .footer-brand::before {
        content: '// ';
        color: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.8);
      }

      .footer-note {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .footer-contact {
        font-size: 11px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      }

      .footer-contact a {
        color: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.8);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .footer-contact a:hover {
        color: #22c55e;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .container {
          margin: 8px;
          border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .content {
          padding: 20px;
        }

        .feedback-hero {
          padding: 24px 16px;
        }

        .feedback-title {
          font-size: 22px;
        }

        .cta-section {
          padding: 20px 16px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <div class='logo'>CS Guild</div>
        <h1>Event Feedback Request</h1>
      </div>

      <div class='content'>
        <div class='feedback-hero'>
          <span class='feedback-icon'>🎉</span>
          <h2 class='feedback-title'>Thank You for Attending!</h2>
          <p class='feedback-subtitle'>Your feedback shapes our future</p>
        </div>

        <div class='event-title'>{{eventTitle}}</div>

        <p class='greeting'>Hi {{firstName}},</p>

        <p class='description'>
          Thank you for attending
          <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong>! We hope you found the event valuable,
          engaging, and worth your time.
        </p>

        <div class='highlight'>
          <h3>Your Voice Matters</h3>
          <p class='description'>
            As you've met the minimum attendance requirement, we'd love to hear
            about your experience. Your feedback helps us improve future events
            and create better experiences for our community of developers and
            learners.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class='description'>
          Please take a few minutes to share your thoughts by clicking the
          button below. Your insights will help us:
        </p>

        <ul
          style='color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); margin: 16px 0 24px 20px; line-height: 1.8;'
        >
          <li>📈 Improve future event content and format</li>
          <li>🎯 Better understand what our community values</li>
          <li>🚀 Plan more engaging workshops and sessions</li>
          <li>🤝 Foster stronger connections within our developer community</li>
        </ul>

        <div class='cta-section'>
          <a href='{{feedbackUrl}}' class='cta-button'>
            🎯 Provide Feedback
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class='organizer-info'>
          <p>This feedback form was created by
            <span class='organizer-name'>{{organizerName}}</span>
            and is specifically tailored for this event.</p>
        </div>

        <div class='security-note'>
          This feedback link is unique to you and this event. Please do not
          share it with others.
        </div>

        <p class='description'>
          Thank you again for being part of our community and contributing to
          the learning environment we're building together!
        </p>

        <p class='description'>
          <strong>Best regards,</strong><br />
          The
          {{organizationName}}
          Team
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        <div class='footer-brand'>Built with ❤️ by {{organizationName}}</div>
        <p class='footer-note'>Empowering the next generation of developers</p>
        <p class='footer-contact'>
          Need help? Contact us at
          <a href='mailto:{{supportEmail}}'>{{supportEmail}}</a>
        </p>
        <br />
        <p class='footer-contact'>
          console.log("Thanks for your feedback! 🚀");
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>